bzperi (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of BzPeri - Modern C++20 Bluetooth LE GATT server library
  * Based on the original Gobbledegook library by Paul Nettle
  * Modernized for BlueZ 5.77+ with D-Bus interface migration
  * C++20 features including std::expected error handling
  * Enhanced connection stability and bondable configuration
  * Linux-specific performance optimizations
  * Backward compatibility with original Gobbledegook API

